<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22121.Imperial_Life_in_the_Emerald_City"><img alt="Imperial Life in the Emerald City: Inside Iraq&#39;s Green Zone" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388184155l/22121._SY160_.jpg" />
